{"settings":"{
    "editor.bracketPairColorization.independentColorPoolPerBracketType": true,
    "git.autofetch": true,
    "[php]": {
        "editor.defaultFormatter": "DEVSENSE.phptools-vscode"
    },
    "php.executablePath": "c:/tools/php82/php.exe",
    "php.hover.fullname": true,
    "editor.fontSize": 13,
    "[latex]": {
        "editor.defaultFormatter": "James-Yu.latex-workshop"
    },
    "[markdown]": {
        "editor.defaultFormatter": "yzhang.markdown-all-in-one"
    },
    "editor.stickyScroll.enabled": false,
    "cSpell.userWords": [
        "Aotearoa",
        "Aripriprazole",
        "Ātaahua",
        "benzatropine",
        "biblabel",
        "clubpenalty",
        "doublespacing",
        "endignore",
        "enumiv",
        "Estrogel",
        "hauora",
        "Kāore",
        "karakia",
        "Karekau",
        "kaupapa",
        "konā",
        "konei",
        "labelfont",
        "labelsep",
        "Lactulose",
        "leiti",
        "Leuprorelin",
        "Likert",
        "Manatū",
        "Medsafe",
        "Mīharo",
        "mkboth",
        "mōhio",
        "mōrena",
        "MVPFAFF",
        "nocte",
        "noitemerr",
        "olds",
        "openbib",
        "Pākeha",
        "Papatūānuku",
        "Pasifika",
        "PATHA",
        "Perindopril",
        "PHARMAC",
        "Qualtrics",
        "rawa",
        "rawe",
        "Rōpū",
        "singlelinecheck",
        "sneakers",
        "takatāpui",
        "tamariki",
        "Tangata",
        "taonga",
        "tēnā",
        "textfont",
        "thebibliography",
        "tika",
        "tikanga",
        "Tino",
        "Tiriti",
        "vaccinators",
        "Wāhine",
        "wehi",
        "whaiora",
        "whakaae",
        "Whakamana",
        "Whanau",
        "whānau",
        "Whare"
    ],
    "cSpell.language": "en-GB",
    "cSpell.showAutocompleteSuggestions": true,
    "git.confirmSync": false,
    "workbench.iconTheme": "material-icon-theme",
    "latex-workshop.latex.recipes": [

        {
            "name": "latexmk",
            "tools": [
                "latexmk"
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "latexmk (latexmkrc)",
            "tools": [
                "latexmk_rconly"
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "latexmk (lualatex)",
            "tools": [
                "lualatexmk"
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "latexmk (xelatex)",
            "tools": [
                "xelatexmk"
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "pdflatex -> bibtex -> pdflatex * 2",
            "tools": [
                "pdflatex",
                "bibtex",
                "pdflatex",
                "pdflatex"
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Compile Rnw files",
            "tools": [
                "rnw2tex",
                "latexmk"
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Compile Jnw files",
            "tools": [
                "jnw2tex",
                "latexmk"
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Compile Pnw files",
            "tools": [
                "pnw2tex",
                "latexmk"
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "tectonic",
            "tools": [
                "tectonic"
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "pdflatex, makeglossaries, pdflatex (2x)",
            "tools": [
                "pdflatex",
                "makeglossaries",
                "pdflatex",
                "pdflatex"
            ]
        },
    ]
    ,
    "latex-workshop.latex.tools": [
  {
    "name": "latexmk",
    "command": "latexmk",
    "args": [
      "-synctex=1",
      "-interaction=nonstopmode",
      "-file-line-error",
      "-pdf",
      "-outdir=%OUTDIR%",
      "%DOC%"
    ],
    "env": {}
  },
  {
    "name": "pdflatex",
    "command": "pdflatex",
    "args": [
      "-synctex=1",
      "-interaction=nonstopmode",
      "-file-line-error",
      "%DOC%"
    ],
    "env": {}
  },
  {
    "name": "bibtex",
    "command": "bibtex",
    "args": [
      "%DOCFILE%"
    ],
    "env": {}
  },
  {
    "name": "pdflatex",
    "command": "pdflatex",
    "args": [
        "-synctex=1",
        "-interaction=nonstopmode",
        "-file-line-error",
        "%DOC%"
    ]
},
{
    "name": "makeglossaries",
    "command": "makeglossaries",
    "args": [
      "%DOCFILE%"
    ]
  }
],
"latex-workshop.latex.autoBuild.run": "onSave",
"latex-workshop.view.pdf.color.dark.pageColorsBackground": "#ffffff",
"latex-workshop.view.pdf.color.light.pageColorsBackground": "#ffffff",
"latex-workshop.view.pdf.color.light.pageColorsForeground": "#ffffff",
"latex-workshop.view.pdf.color.dark.pageColorsForeground": "#ffffff",
"latex-workshop.view.pdf.hand": true,
"workbench.productIconTheme": "material-product-icons",
"workbench.colorTheme": "Catppuccin Macchiato",
"catppuccin.accentColor": "blue",
"editor.semanticHighlighting.enabled": true,
"terminal.integrated.minimumContrastRatio": 1,
"window.titleBarStyle": "custom",
"latex-workshop.formatting.latex": "latexindent",
"latex-workshop.intellisense.citation.backend": "biblatex",
"latex-utilities.liveReformat.enabled": true,
"latex-utilities.zotero.citeMethod": "vscode",
"terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.linux": "zsh",
"terminal.explorerKind": "external",
"terminal.integrated.fontFamily": "MesloLGS NF",
"[astro]": {
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "astro-build.astro-vscode"
},
"[json]": {
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode"
},
"[typescript]": {
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode"
},
"liveshare.allowGuestDebugControl": true,
"liveshare.allowGuestTaskControl": true,
"git.enableSmartCommit": true,
"workbench.settings.applyToAllProfiles": [
    "editor.fontFamily"
],
"editor.fontFamily": "fira code ",
"workbench.secondarySideBar.defaultVisibility": "hidden",
"security.workspace.trust.untrustedFiles": "open",
}"}
